Description: Provides a workflow for exploring World Development Indicators (WDI) country-level panel data. It downloads the WDI data using the 'WDI' package and compute diagnostic indices that captures the temporal behaviours of the data by incorporating the grouping structure of the data.
    The set of diagnostic indices implemented includes; variation features, trend and shape features and sequential temporal features.
